          Project Folder Structure
        </div>
      </div>
      <b class="mt-2 pl-2 text-sm font-bold">The Extractor</b>
      <div
        class="ml-2 cursor-pointer rounded-lg bg-opacity-50 px-2 py-1 hover:bg-neutral-800"
        style="text-shadow: 0 0 1rem white;"
      >
        Setup Environment
      </div>
      <div
        class="ml-2 cursor-pointer rounded-lg bg-opacity-50 px-2 py-1 hover:bg-neutral-800"
        style="text-shadow: 0 0 1rem white;"
